{
  "texts": [
    "This goal is related to fields where end users are extremely important, and their ability to interact with models is what ensures success.",
    "We must foster trust by ensuring that AI is consistent with human values and expertise.",
    "Furthermore, it is critical to incorporate user feedback and leverage human expertise in decision-making to improve model performance.",
    "Traditional XAI approaches, on the other hand, perform based on lower-level attributes such as pixel intensities, which do not correspond with human rational thinking, and they have significant limitations in communicating with domain experts [69].Ethical AI: Ethical consideration, also known as fairness [23], refers to an AI system that makes decisions that are unbiased.",
    "Its goal is to address biases in AI decision-making and promote fairness, as well as to support ethical standards in AI development and deployment."
  ]
}